WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.906
"The Voice Kids fridays on SAT.1 and on YouTube."

00:00:00.360 --> 00:00:05.780
(Speaker) "Maira is accompanied by her mother's best Brazilian wishes."

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:08.494
"... and by herself on the piano."

00:01:29.440 --> 00:01:31.440
(Thore) "Come on, Tim, do it as well."

00:01:59.716 --> 00:02:01.716
(Lena) "Nooo."

00:02:13.915 --> 00:02:15.915
(Maira) "Thank you."

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:18.480
(Henning) "That's a cheap move, dude."

00:02:23.688 --> 00:02:25.688
(Lena) "What's your name?"

00:02:25.688 --> 00:02:26.335
(Maira) "Maira."

00:02:26.335 --> 00:02:27.465
(Lena) "How do you feel?"

00:02:27.465 --> 00:02:29.215
(Maira) "I'm totally happy."

00:02:29.215 --> 00:02:30.517
(Tim) "We are happy as well."

00:02:33.700 --> 00:02:35.360
(Lena) "Does the tension fall from your shoulders?"

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:36.713
(Maira) "Yes, totally."

00:02:38.740 --> 00:02:40.740
(Lena) "A lot of big respect for you that you sang and played the piano."

00:02:40.848 --> 00:02:42.848
(Maira) "Thank you."

00:02:42.848 --> 00:02:43.920
(Lena) "How old are you?"

00:02:43.920 --> 00:02:44.420
(Maira) "I'm thirteen years old."

00:02:49.680 --> 00:02:51.680
(Lena) "Wow. You sang beautifully as well as ...."

00:02:56.507 --> 00:02:58.507
"Ok. So next one. I can't talk any longer. I'm wrecked. You were fantastic."

00:02:58.507 --> 00:03:00.400
"Join my team."

00:03:01.860 --> 00:03:04.380
(Tim) "I pushed the button later than the others."

00:03:04.440 --> 00:03:05.240
(Maira) "Yes."

00:03:05.300 --> 00:03:07.760
(Tim) "This had only one reason, I want to enjoy it longer."

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:08.260
(Lena) "Of course."

00:03:09.460 --> 00:03:14.440
(Tim) "It was wonderful. I could have never gone on stage with an instrument."

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:17.340
"I would have been to scared and would forget to sing. Big respect for you."

00:03:17.474 --> 00:03:19.474
(Maira) "Thank you."

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:32.840
(Henning) "Actually, I just have one statement for you. First, thank you very, very much."

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.960
"May I borrow that for a second?"

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:44.440
(Henning) "When you sing for me ..."

00:03:44.440 --> 00:03:46.880
"... I can't think of anything to say."

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:52.080
"If you want to choose me."

00:03:52.120 --> 00:03:54.120
"It can be forever."

00:03:57.200 --> 00:04:02.220
"I give you everything of me. That is my promise." 

00:04:03.060 --> 00:04:08.240
"Every day without you a crime."

00:04:08.320 --> 00:04:14.080
"I love high suspense and most of the time I'm full of energy."

00:04:14.600 --> 00:04:23.760
"And we celebrate your victory in Panik-style in St. Peter's Basilica."

00:04:23.760 --> 00:04:26.900
(Henning) "That is everything I can say. You are wonderful."

00:04:26.900 --> 00:04:28.015
"Don't let the pressure get to you."

00:04:28.015 --> 00:04:29.221
 "Let your heart decide."

00:04:43.215 --> 00:04:45.215
(Maira) "I choose Henning."

00:05:01.314 --> 00:05:04.254
(Maira) "All three of them turned around. Oh my God."

00:05:04.380 --> 00:05:06.900
"And Henning sang me a song."

